	(text "x2 USB-C Cameras (HUB 1 & 2)\nx1 USB-C RTK (off-board 2.0 port)\n1x USB Serial Converter for IMU (off-board 2.0 port)\nx2 ESP32 (Motor Controller, Camera Triggering) (HUB 3 & 4)\nx1 RJ45 Connector (LIDAR) (PCIE)\n\n1x (or 2x) USB-C to route both PCIE and USB-HUB to B-Key Port.\n\nx1 Buck Converter 19V - 5V (USB Power)\n1x Reverse Voltage Protection."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 175.514 35.306 0)
